# subLocality

**Instance Property**

The name of the area within the locality.

## Declaration

```swift
subLocality?: string;
```

## Discussion

For example, the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/SearchAutocompleteResult/subLocality] for the Golden Gate Park is `"Golden Gate Park"`.
